## Admin UI Features

- **Gradient hero header** with Import Legacy + Add Course buttons
- **4 stat cards**: Total Courses, Active, Diplomas, Certificates
- **Searchable/filterable table** with type badges, toggle switches, student counts
- **3-tab modal** (Basic Info / Website Content / Pricing)
- **Offer config**: toggle, price, label, validity, seat limit
- **Safety**: soft-disables courses with enrolled students instead of hard delete

## First-Time Setup

After deploy, admin should click **"Import Legacy"** button to migrate the 22 hardcoded courses + any existing CoursePricing data into the Program collection.

